   554→## Notes
   555→
   556→### Critical Dependencies
   557→- **lib/paths.ts** must be updated FIRST - all other files depend on it
   558→- **lib/TraceEmitter.ts** affects observability and monitoring
   559→- All hooks that write files must ensure directories exist
   560→
   561→### Windows Path Limitations
   562→
   563→1. **MAX_PATH (260 characters)**
   564→   - Enable long paths in Windows 10/11:
   565→     ```powershell
   566→     # Enable long path support (requires Admin)
   567→     New-ItemProperty -Path "HKLM:\SYSTEM\CurrentControlSet\Control\FileSystem" -Name "LongPathsEnabled" -Value 1 -PropertyType DWORD -Force
   568→     ```
   569→
   570→2. **Invalid Characters**
   571→   - Avoid: `< > : " / \ | ? *`
   572→   - Replace in filenames: `:` → `-`, `/` → `-`, `\` → `-`
   573→
   574→3. **Reserved Names**
   575→   - Avoid: CON, PRN, AUX, NUL, COM1-COM9, LPT1-LPT9
   576→
   577→4. **Drive Letters**
   578→   - Never hardcode drive letters (C:, D:)
   579→   - Use environment variables: `USERPROFILE`, `TEMP`, `APPDATA`
   580→
   581→### File System Differences
   582→
   583→| Feature | Unix | Windows | Solution |
   584→|---------|------|---------|----------|
   585→| Path Separator | `/` | `\` | Use `path.join()` |
   586→| Home Dir | `$HOME` | `%USERPROFILE%` | `os.homedir()` |
   587→| Temp Dir | `/tmp` | `%TEMP%` | `os.tmpdir()` |
   588→| Symlinks | Native | Limited (Admin) | Use junctions or copy |
   589→| Permissions | chmod/chown | ACLs | Use Windows APIs or skip |
   590→| Line Endings | `\n` | `\r\n` | Normalize to `\n` |
   591→| Case Sensitive | Yes | No | Use case-insensitive compares |
   592→
   593→### Performance Considerations
   594→
   595→1. **File System Operations**
   596→   - Use `fs.mkdirSync(dir, { recursive: true })` instead of multiple calls
   597→   - Batch file writes to reduce I/O
   598→
   599→2. **Process Spawning**
   600→   - Reuse process handles where possible
   601→   - Use `shell: true` on Windows for command resolution
   602→
   603→3. **Path Operations**
   604→   - Cache resolved paths
   605→   - Use `path.join()` instead of string concatenation
   606→
